snippet.title: The funniest and most humorous animal moments on Earth - Funny animal compilation
snippet.description:
World would be very empty without animals. Animals make us happy and laugh! Just look how these cats, kittens, dogs, puppies, cows, squirrels, raccoons sleep, eat, make funny faces and noises, play, get scared,... So funny, hilarious and cute! What is your favourite clip? :) Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!
